Map by Buttons

Made for Robin
-----
Zm_Breakfloor_Checkerboard

There is around 520 breakable squares. Around 496 of them are large and cannot be climbed. The other (about) 4 squares cover the whole map width/length.

Large square HP: 50
Larger square HP: 75

There is also lava at the bottom of the map.
